== AsakusaSatellite

AsakusaSatellite is a realtime chat application.

=== Authors
* @suer
* @mallowlabs
* @mzp

=== Requirement
* Ruby 1.8.7
* groonga (1.0.6 or lator)

=== Install
 $ bundle install --path vendor/bundle
 $ rake groonga:migrate

=== Install for Developer
 $ cp bleis-hooks/* .git/hooks

=== Access
 $ rails server
 $ ruby websocket/server
access to http://localhost:3000/chat/tweet

=== Test
* setup
 $ rake groonga:migrate RAILS_ENV=test

* indivisual testing
 $ ruby spec/{controller,model}/$(name)_spec.rb

* test all
 $ rake spec

* run with rcov
 $ rake spec:rcov

